translationBlock.key: Manually triggers bound events. The event object passed to this function is sent directly as-is to the bound events. Check the documentation for each event to see what is required. No checks will be done on the data here, but it is not recommended to fail to send all parameters required. If serverWide is true, the event is triggered directly in the server, unless it is a CommandHelper specific event, in which case, serverWide is irrelevant. Defaults to false, which means that only CommandHelper code will receive the event.
